msgid "KDE Linux"
msgstr "KDE Linux"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.linux.metainfo.xml:9
msgid ""
"A modern Linux distribution focused on the KDE Plasma desktop environment"
msgstr ""
"Une distribution Linux moderne reposant sur l'environnement de bureau KDE "
"Plasma"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.linux.metainfo.xml:14
msgid ""
"KDE Linux is a user-friendly operating system built around the KDE Plasma "
"desktop environment. It provides a complete computing experience with a "
"focus on productivity, customization, and ease of use."
msgstr ""
"KDE Linux est un système d'exploitation convivial construit à partir de "
"l'environnement de bureau KDE Plasma. Il offre une expérience informatique "
"globale, en mettant l'accent sur la productivité, la personnalisation et "
"l'ergonomie."

